00:00:16,456 --> 00:00:21,656
Let's confirm if he has red blood flowing through him too.

6
00:00:21,656 --> 00:00:24,856
Fortunately, the museum will be closed next Sunday.

7
00:00:24,856 --> 00:00:28,956
None of the staff beside us will show up.

8
00:00:28,956 --> 00:00:30,356
Great.

9
00:00:30,356 --> 00:00:33,056
The sooner the better.

10
00:00:33,056 --> 00:00:35,656
That reminds me, Mr. Seikanji.

11
00:00:35,656 --> 00:00:39,956
The deadline for repaying the loan is closing in, isn't it?

12
00:00:39,956 --> 00:00:41,356
What...

13
00:00:41,356 --> 00:00:42,656
Look who's talking.

14
00:00:42,656 --> 00:00:44,956
I heard that you embezzled money, and it was exposed,

15
00:00:44,956 --> 00:00:48,456
