16
00:00:48,456 --> 00:00:50,056
I don't want to be told that by a manager

17
00:00:50,056 --> 00:00:52,656
who fell for junk stocks and incurred a huge loss.

18
00:00:52,656 --> 00:00:54,956
So, I'm the only one

19
00:00:54,956 --> 00:00:59,356
that doesn't have to rush to finish things off.

20
00:00:59,356 --> 00:01:01,156
Is that so?

21
00:01:01,156 --> 00:01:04,656
As his ex-girlfriend, I'll bet you're worried about

22
00:01:04,656 --> 00:01:08,256
when your inheritance deed will go down the drain.

23
00:01:08,256 --> 00:01:13,556
Come now, there's no use arguing now.

24
00:01:13,556 --> 00:01:18,056
We've got only one common purpose to pursue.

25
00:01:18,056 --> 00:01:21,756
That is, to murder Jisaburo Izumi.

26
00:01:21,756 --> 00:01:26,156
That's why we're gathered here, aren't we?

27
00:01:26,156 --> 00:01:30,156
So, I'd like to confirm with you one more time, Moyono.

28
00:01:30,156 --> 00:01:33,556
In case we succeed in murdering Jisaburo,

29
00:01:33,556 --> 00:01:36,956
we split half the inheritance that is due to you

30
00:01:36,956 --> 00:01:39,056
among us three.

31
00:01:39,056 --> 00:01:42,856
The one who actually succeeds in killing him gets 80%,

32
00:01:42,856 --> 00:01:45,056
and the remaining two gets 10% each

33
00:01:45,056 --> 00:01:47,956
to keep their mouths shut.

34
00:01:47,956 --> 00:01:51,656
I kind of feel like I'm the only one who's losing out.

35
00:01:51,656 --> 00:01:53,556
But, I guess it can't be helped.

36
00:01:53,556 --> 00:01:56,556
Because if I do it alone and fail,

37
00:01:56,556 --> 00:01:58,656
everything'll go to pieces.

38
00:01:58,656 --> 00:02:00,956
If all three of us pitch in, the odds of succeeding

39
00:02:00,956 --> 00:02:03,456
would be greater.

40
00:02:03,456 --> 00:02:09,256
Okay. Then, we'll launch the plan next Sunday.

41
00:02:22,056 --> 00:02:23,956
Aim for a 100% solution.

42
00:02:23,956 --> 00:02:26,056
Clear all mysteries and codes.

43
00:02:26,056 --> 00:02:27,956
A dangerous conversation at the Noh Mask Museum.

44
00:02:27,956 --> 00:02:30,356
The secret of the threesome hiding behind the mask.

45
00:02:30,356 --> 00:02:31,956
He sees through the one and only truth.

46
00:02:31,956 --> 00:02:33,756
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

47
00:02:33,756 --> 00:02:36,556
His name is Detective Conan!

48
00:04:17,152 --> 00:04:22,952
"The Ogre Dances in the Noh Mask Mansion (Part 1)"

49
00:04:30,852 --> 00:04:34,052
Huh? It seems to be closed today.

50
00:04:34,052 --> 00:04:35,452
Oh, yeah.

51
00:04:36,252 --> 00:04:38,852
Never mind, this is an emergency.

52
00:04:40,652 --> 00:04:41,652
Yes?

53
00:04:41,652 --> 00:04:44,152
I would like to see the director!

54
00:04:44,152 --> 00:04:45,852
I'm sorry.

55
00:04:45,852 --> 00:04:50,752
We're closed today so Director Izumi resting today.

56
00:04:50,752 --> 00:04:54,252
Excuse me. I'm Naruya Akaza.

57
00:04:54,252 --> 00:04:57,352
I have an appointment with Mr. Izumi.

58
00:05:02,252 --> 00:05:05,252
Oh, Ms. Moyono Mibu?

59
00:05:05,252 --> 00:05:07,652
Long time no see.

60
00:05:09,252 --> 00:05:12,052
I'll open the front door right now.

61
00:05:20,852 --> 00:05:23,652
I can't let you in.

62
00:05:23,652 --> 00:05:25,452
Like I just told you a while ago,

63
00:05:25,452 --> 00:05:27,652
